<section class="page">
  <div class="wrap narrow">
    <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
    <h1 class="mt-2 mb-3">A better home for the lifestyle</h1>
    <p class="page-lead" style="font-size:1.15rem">
      <%= brand.name %> was built for open-minded couples and singles who were tired of
      clunky, dated platforms that treat privacy as an afterthought. We started from scratch
      with three principles: <strong class="text-gold">discretion, taste, and trust</strong>.
    </p>

    <div class="deco-rule"><span>How it works</span></div>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature card card-pad">
        <div class="ficon">①</div><h3>Create your profile</h3>
        <p>Couples add both partners. Singles verify their age. Say who you are and who you'd like to meet.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature card card-pad">
        <div class="ficon">②</div><h3>Control your photos</h3>
        <p>Show a public face — or none. Keep private photos locked and grant access one member at a time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature card card-pad">
        <div class="ficon">③</div><h3>Connect &amp; meet</h3>
        <p>Like, match, message, and RSVP to events near you. Real connections, on your terms.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="deco-rule"><span>Our promise</span></div>
    <p class="about-block" style="margin-top:0">
We don't sell your data. We don't spam you with pop-ups. We review every report.
And we're building the features the community actually asks for — not the ones that
squeeze the most clicks out of you.

Welcome to the lifestyle, elevated.
    </p>

    <div class="center mt-5">
      <a href="/enter" class="btn btn-primary">Create your free profile</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
